====Usage notes====
* When the object of the verb is a person, 爱 usually refers to romantic love.  When used like this, older Mandarin speakers often describe the use of this term as overly [[肉麻]] (''adj.'' something that gives you the creeps, extremely melodramatic).  For this reason, the word {{zh-l|喜歡/喜欢}} (to like) might be used instead.  The word 喜欢 literally means "to like", but when used in a romantic context, can (but does not always) mean "to love."  However, Mandarin speakers born since the 1970s are now using the verb 爱 much more often than was socially acceptable in the past.

